{"tid":1698892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人必須認清一個事實","createTime":"2019-11-07T23:07:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T13:05:01.000Z","uid":27725,"like":162,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"c4a14c029d530e226aaf11dcb4b18fd1fe5d57f3","tid":1698892,"uid":27725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T23:07:21.000Z","msg":"開始咗依場運動 <br />\n我哋依家前面得返兩條路 攬炒或集中營<br />\n我哋每一位必須有決心 唔好諗住你可以倖免 唔好諗住靠人哋<br />\n你依家對付緊嘅係一個強權國家 殺人政權<br />\n依幾個月都講咗好耐 有板你睇 六四 新疆 <br />\n唔好諗住自己有退路 中共係唔會放過我哋任何一個<br />\n叫口號唔係得個叫字 諗清楚個意思<br />\n參與呢場運動 唔係由情緒去主導你參與 係你對民主嘅堅持<br />\n<br />\n面對自己嘅缺點！勇又唔夠人哋勇 所以！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">三罷係唯一出路</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明依家三罷 成個方向同計劃都出晒黎<br />\n唔夠勇武冇問題<br />\n三罷係一件只需要團結同決心嘅事 咁今次可唔可以爭氣啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c60b52da6ef92b1483372166e205468e2433618","tid":1698892,"uid":27725,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T23:08:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GOU6DSj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGOU6DSj.jpg&h=1295672e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/puyZYSk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpuyZYSk.jpg&h=b8a79a13&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jrHHcck.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjrHHcck.jpg&h=59a7affe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bc54b9934ad9bcdefde26ca00eb407d3a82cd6e3","tid":1698892,"uid":27725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T23:09:03.000Z","msg":"🔴二百萬三罷聯合陣線🔴<br />\n抗爭 | 工會 | 罷工 | 行業行動