pid":"35e2933e645799189aed9aec17f420dafd0663ed","tid":1698892,"uid":27725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T23:14:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4b4197427c7d4f7be6c19a3c33ba740d75c25f4e","tid":1698892,"uid":146030,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T23:18:47.000Z","msg":"所以我已經放棄咗香港<br />\n一個殺人放火姦淫擄掠做齊嘅政權<br />\n再打落去 死傷人數一定係幾何級數上升<br />\n我覺得有手足係唔怕死 但係真係要諗吓值唔值得為呢班冷血，死咁多人都無動於衷嘅人付出咁多，所有手足係唔應該受嘅咁嘅嘢<br />\nBno平權在即，我最大心願係救得一個得一個，希望所有手足們可以倫敦相擁"},{"pid":"a65ed30f0e9fd6faa85ba8b5623cd4328759b9b3","tid":1698892,"uid":27725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T23:26:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c40bbb12251f0f0df3a583a370a386eecdf970a3","tid":1698892,"uid":146030,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T23:29:26.000Z","msg":"理性咁睇 我睇唔到短期內有贏嘅機會<br />\n拖長嚟玩嘅話 分分鐘係數以年計 依家呢段時間日日都會有手足比人打比人殺<br />\n我唔想手足咁樣 香港人唔應該受<br />\n唔好話我放負 我係講事實 雖然好殘酷"},{"pid":"5746d5ccd721fcdad79d9387fa04cf140d3ada6a","tid":1698892,"uid":27725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T23:29:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5a7692227ad87f56bbb246deca6744f8ba935ac1","tid":1698892,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T23:30:46.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，推post &amp; 借個靚位<br />\n<br />\n******眾籌*******<br />\n鐘庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 (eg. 721, 831) &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先52%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持)<br />\n<br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">h